data.description: Great opportunity: 7,500 sq.ft lot in East Little Havana. Excellent rectangular lot overlooking 4th St., 4 blocks from the Walk of Fame at historical 8th St. Walk to the action, go to the famous 8th Street Latin Carnival and leave your car safely parked at home. South Beach is 13 minutes away. Downtown Miami and Brickell are 10 minutes away. This is a two story fourplex, zoned multifamily. There is commercial zoning in the same block. All legal, no violations. Zoned T4-L. 4 electric meters. Four gas meters. Parking for 10+ vehicles. Great opportunity. Conventional loan available: only 5% down payment for owner occupied buyers.
